/* =============================================================================                                                                                
Program     : DRG_Formats.txt                                                                                                                                   
Date Revised: 09/28/2017                                                                                                                                        
Descripiton :                                                                                                                                                   
Create SAS formats that may be used with SAS procedures to label the values of                                                                                  
Medicare DRGs.  For example, the following SAS statements use the DRGV33F format                                                                                
with the Freq Procedure to label the values of DRG33 in the frequency listing:                                                                                  
                                                                                                                                                                
    Proc Freq Data = NIS_2015q1q3_CORE ;                                                                                                                        
         Table DRG33 ;                                                                                                                                          
         Format DRG33 DRGV33F. ;                                                                                                                                
    Run ;                                                                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                
The DRGnnMDC formats (where nn is the DRG version) map DRGs to MDCs.  For example,                                                                              
the following SAS statement uses the DRG33MDC format to assign an MDC from a                                                                                    
version 33 (effective 10/01/2015) DRG:                                                                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                                
    MDC_NoPOA = Input(Put(DRG_NoPOA, DRG33MDC.), 2.) ;                                                                                                                                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
The DRGnnMSF formats (where nn is the DRG version) map DRGs to indicators with                                                                                                                                                                  
values "M" for Medical or "P" for Surgical.  For example, the following SAS                                                                                                                                                                     
statement uses the DRG33MSF format to assign the Medical / Surgical Flag for a                                                                                                                                                                  
version 33 (effective 10/01/2015) DRG:                                                                                                                                                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
    DRGMSFlag = Put(DRG, DRG33MSF.) ;                                                                                                                                                                                                           
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
The following tables list formats available for selected HCUP data elements.                                                                                                                                                                    
(Note that some data elements are not available for all years.)                                                                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
    Core File                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
    Data Element(s)         Format Name(s)                                                                                                                                                                                                      
    ===============         ==============                                                                                                                                                                                                      
    DRG, DRG_NoPOA          DRGVnnF.  (where nn is the applicable DRG version number)                                                                                                                                                           
    DRG18                   DRGv18f.                                                                                                                                                                                                            
    DRG24                   DRGv24f.                                                                                                                                                                                                            
    DRG, DRG_NoPOA          DRGnnMDC. (where nn is the applicable DRG version number)                                                                                                                                                           
    DRG, DRG_NoPOA          DRGnnMSF. (where nn is the applicable DRG version number)                                                                                                                                                           
    DRGVER                  FDRGVER.                                                                                                                                                                                                            
    MDC, MDC_NoPOA          MDCVnnF.  (where nn is the applicable DRG version number)                                                                                                                                                           
    MDC18                   MDCv18f.                                                                                                                                                                                                            
    MDC24                   MDCv24f.                                                                                                                                                                                                            
============================================================================= */                                                                                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                
PROC FORMAT ;                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
Value FDRGVER /* DRGVER - Medicare DRG Version */
    5 = ' 5: Effective 10/01/1987'
    6 = ' 6: Effective 10/01/1988'
    7 = ' 7: Effective 10/01/1989'
    8 = ' 8: Effective 10/01/1990'
    9 = ' 9: Effective 10/01/1991'
   10 = '10: Effective 10/01/1992'
   11 = '11: Effective 10/01/1993'
   12 = '12: Effective 10/01/1994'
   13 = '13: Effective 10/01/1995'
   14 = '14: Effective 10/01/1996'
   15 = '15: Effective 10/01/1997'
   16 = '16: Effective 10/01/1998'
   17 = '17: Effective 10/01/1999'
   18 = '18: Effective 10/01/2000'
   19 = '19: Effective 10/01/2001'
   20 = '20: Effective 10/01/2002'
   21 = '21: Effective 10/01/2003'
   22 = '22: Effective 10/01/2004'
   23 = '23: Effective 10/01/2005'
   24 = '24: Effective 10/01/2006'
   25 = '25: Effective 10/01/2007'
   26 = '26: Effective 10/01/2008'
   27 = '27: Effective 10/01/2009'
   28 = '28: Effective 10/01/2010'
   29 = '29: Effective 10/01/2011'
   30 = '30: Effective 10/01/2012'
   31 = '31: Effective 10/01/2013'
   32 = '32: Effective 10/01/2014'
   33 = '33: Effective 10/01/2015'
   34 = '34: Effective 10/01/2016'
   ;
